            <h1>Final project proposal</h1>
            
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            
            <p> BurnsBucha </p>
            
            <p> BurnsBucha is a Kombucha beverage company. Kombucha is a fermented, lightly effervescent, sweetened black tea drink commonly consumed for its purported health benefits. We are a small business that provides beverage service to everyone in the US by online services and standard delivery. Our facility is located in San Luis Obispo, every week we will have a booth at our local county farmers market. </p><!--Short description of the company-->
            
            <h2>Target audience</h2>
            
            <p>The people who are going to be using this site are going to be individuals want to expand their kombucha knowledge. Kombucha has multiple health benfits, users who are intersted in the product consist of people who are more aware of what they want to put into their body, expand their "Bucha" pallete and those who like to order products online. Or create their own!</p><!-- Who are the people who use this site? -->
           
            <p>The goal of this website is to expand our business to multiple medias. We want to have people be able to visit our site and be tempted to learn more about the company and order Kombucha across the US.  </p><!-- What are their primary task and goals? -->
            
