					<h2> BurnsBucha, It's alive! ...</h2>
                    <p>BurnsBucha Kombucha can be a healthy alternative to soft drinks, It contains probiotics that can support gut health. - The probiotic microorganisms consume the plant fibers that human bodies cannot digest. This is essential for maintaining a healthy gut biome </p>
                    <p>At BurnsBooch, we celebrate the harmony of traditional kombucha, craft brewing, and fresh-pressed juice. #livecultured</p>

                    <h2>Eat your kombucha, or create your own!</h2>
                    <p> Did you know starter tea alone will brew Kombucha! Thats right, starter tea contains all the benficial bacteria you need to brew Kombucha.</p>
                   
